name: Space Traveler (ThirtyEight Studios)
description:
Hi, Kaapo here, this is my first ever game so please do not judge me.

The game is about a spaceship which is travelling across the space and you have to avoid obstacles and earn coins to get points.

As i say in the credits of the game, most of the artworks and sounds are taken from the net so if you recognize something you  own please contact us at staffprogrammers2019@gmail.com
